pl.bristleback.server.bristle.authorisation.user
Class UsersContainer

java.lang.Object
  pl.bristleback.server.bristle.authorisation.user.UsersContainer

@Component
public class UsersContainer
extends java.lang.Object

Class holding references to all currently connected users. Manages connection between frameworks based abstraction of user (IdentifiedUser) and WebSocket internal implementation (WebsocketConnector). Provides convenient methods for transforming IdentifiedUser to WebsocketConnector and vice-versa.

Author:
Pawel Machowski created at 01.05.12 14:04
